unit FCRC32;

{32 Bit CRC, fast 4KB table version, polynomial (used in zip and others)}


interface

(*************************************************************************

 DESCRIPTION     :  32 Bit CRC

 REQUIREMENTS    :  TP6/7, D1-D7/D9-D10/D12/D17-D18/D25S, FPC, VP

 EXTERNAL DATA   :  ---

 MEMORY USAGE    :  ---

